               <p>SARAH WESTON. I am servant to Mr. John Weight. On the 19th of March, about eight o'clock in the morning, I saw the prisoner take the carpet out of the shop-window, and told my master.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18170416-131-person1017">
